I am a Real World Evidence (RWE) Data Scientist and Statistician with more than 18 years of experience in academia and industry combined. Currently, as a Principal Data Scientist at ConcertAI, I provide strategic guidance for the use of real world data, their validations, and use of algorithms to derive real world evidence (RWE) for evaluation of drugs and biologics.


Interests
Statistical Inference
Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence in healthcare
Big data analysis
Public health research